30
00:02:15,020 --> 00:02:15,390
Come on.

31
00:02:17,440 --> 00:02:17,900
Let's go.

32
00:02:19,020 --> 00:02:19,300
Okay.

33
00:02:19,510 --> 00:02:19,990
I'll try.

34
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:20,560
Let's go.

35
00:02:22,460 --> 00:02:22,830
Huan'er,

36
00:02:22,860 --> 00:02:24,390
