37
00:02:24,860 --> 00:02:25,670
Computer Science.

38
00:02:26,300 --> 00:02:27,700
Computer Science?

39
00:02:27,700 --> 00:02:29,620
So he's going to be a programmer, right?

40
00:02:31,300 --> 00:02:32,510
I don't know what he'll do

41
