in the future.

42
00:02:35,110 --> 00:02:36,140
Aren't programmers

43
00:02:36,140 --> 00:02:37,180
all those

44
00:02:37,350 --> 00:02:37,950
nerdy types,

45
00:02:38,020 --> 00:02:39,350
wearing black-rimmed glasses,

46
00:02:39,350 --> 00:02:40,390
checkered shirts,

47
00:02:40,510 --> 00:02:41,580
and always looking serious?

48
00:02:43,140 --> 00:02:44,180
Is he nerdy?

49
00:02:44,270 --> 00:02:45,020
I don't know.

50
00:02:45,900 --> 00:02:47,110
However,

51
00:02:47,220 --> 00:02:48,180
