52
00:02:48,180 --> 00:02:48,950
He's so handsome!

53
00:02:49,020 --> 00:02:50,060
Take a picture for me!

54
00:02:50,830 --> 00:02:51,580
He's so handsome!

55
00:02:51,700 --> 00:02:52,230
Exactly!

56
00:02:55,230 --> 00:02:57,900
- Nice!
- Nice!

57
00:02:58,270 --> 00:02:59,270
