58
00:02:59,510 --> 00:03:00,270
Run, quick!

59
00:03:11,420 --> 00:03:12,620
Nice shot!

60
00:03:12,620 --> 00:03:14,300
Great!

61
00:03:14,300 --> 00:03:15,350
Nice shot!

62
00:03:15,380 --> 00:03:16,500
