75
00:03:40,180 --> 00:03:40,510
Bye.

76
00:03:42,140 --> 00:03:42,550
Let's go.

77
00:03:45,420 --> 00:03:45,900
Huan'er.

78
00:03:46,350 --> 00:03:47,070
So is this

79
00:03:47,110 --> 00:03:48,070
your programmer friend?

80
00:03:48,510 --> 00:03:50,070
