you'll call me Dad.

85
00:03:57,740 --> 00:03:58,700
You're so fierce!

86
00:03:59,100 --> 00:03:59,830
That's the spirit!

87
00:03:59,840 --> 00:04:01,900
You can't play football
without a bit of aggression.

88
00:04:01,900 --> 00:04:03,150
Stop staring and let's continue.

89
00:04:03,350 --> 00:04:03,950
Stop looking.

90
00:04:03,990 --> 00:04:04,860
Don't be so reluctant.

91
00:04:04,900 --> 00:04:05,640
Come on.

92
00:04:06,960 --> 00:04:08,320
Pass it to me!

93
