94
00:04:17,860 --> 00:04:18,300
Thank you.

95
00:04:22,140 --> 00:04:24,687
(Not bad, but I think Tian Chi
from pharmacy course is more handsome.)

96
00:04:25,150 --> 00:04:25,740
Huan'er.

97
00:04:28,470 --> 00:04:28,910
Look.

98
00:04:30,110 --> 00:04:30,500
This.

99
00:04:30,820 --> 00:04:33,230
Is this your handsome friend
from Computer Science?

100
00:04:33,260 --> 00:04:36,300
