(I want all the information)

103
00:04:42,620 --> 00:04:43,520
(on this football guy.)

104
00:04:43,670 --> 00:04:44,300
(I declare)

105
00:04:44,360 --> 00:04:46,300
(he is the new
heartthrob of Wuan University.)

106
00:04:46,760 --> 00:04:47,470
(He's just okay.)

107
00:04:47,620 --> 00:04:49,300
(I think Tian Chi
from the pharmacy course)

108
00:04:49,300 --> 00:04:50,220
(is more handsome.)

109
00:04:51,420 --> 00:04:51,910
Yes.

110
00:04:55,380 --> 00:04:57,060
Was he very popular

111
00:04:58,300 --> 00:04:59,620
at your high school?

112
00:05:00,860 --> 00:05:02,260
Do you think he's handsome?

113
00:05:03,150 --> 00:05:03,990
Of course!

114
00:05:04,230 --> 00:05:05,420
Honestly,

115
00:05:05,700 --> 00:05:06,820
he's pretty good-looking.

116
00:05:10,590 --> 00:05:11,500
Just be honest,

117
00:05:11,940 --> 00:05:13,710
during the three years as his classmate,

118
00:05:13,860 --> 00:05:15,880
did you ever have
any thoughts about him?

119
00:05:20,230 --> 00:05:20,710
Yes.

120
00:05:21,500 --> 00:05:23,380
Every day I wanted to shoot him,

121
00:05:23,550 --> 00:05:25,230
