126
00:05:32,860 --> 00:05:34,260
is guilt.

127
00:05:34,470 --> 00:05:35,910
That makes so much sense.

128
00:05:36,030 --> 00:05:37,500
Which psychologist said that?

129
00:05:37,590 --> 00:05:38,300
I did.

130
00:05:42,300 --> 00:05:43,350
The student council senior

131
00:05:43,420 --> 00:05:45,470
invited me to a social barbecue.

132
00:05:47,500 --> 00:05:48,110
Why don't you

133
00:05:48,110 --> 00:05:48,670
come with me?

134
00:05:49,500 --> 00:05:50,110
Sure.

135
00:05:50,540 --> 00:05:51,710
Would that be okay, though?

136
00:05:51,860 --> 00:05:52,990
She invited you, not us.

137
00:05:53,060 --> 00:05:54,420
If we go, wouldn't it be...

138
00:05:54,550 --> 00:05:55,110
It's fine.

139
00:05:55,230 --> 00:05:56,500
It's a welcome event, after all.

140
00:05:56,540 --> 00:05:57,880
The more, the merrier.

141
00:05:59,590 --> 00:06:03,150
In that case, I need to sleep early.

142
00:06:03,150 --> 00:06:04,030
So it's settled then.

143
00:06:05,860 --> 00:06:07,300
Where's Dong Huixin?

144
00:06:07,350 --> 00:06:08,710
I haven't seen her all day.

145
00:06:09,350 --> 00:06:10,790
She's really over the top.

146
00:06:12,420 --> 00:06:13,350
Forget it, let's sleep.

147
00:06:13,680 --> 00:06:14,400
Let's sleep.

148
00:06:14,460 --> 00:06:14,910
Good night.

149
00:06:15,300 --> 00:06:16,030
Good night.

150
00:06:29,200 --> 00:06:30,110
(Are you still mad?)

151
00:07:09,740 --> 00:07:10,500
Hello.

152
00:07:12,790 --> 00:07:13,590
Nice to meet you.

153
00:07:13,720 --> 00:07:15,000
Hope we can get along well.

154
00:07:16,110 --> 00:07:17,150
It's late now.

155
00:07:17,520 --> 00:07:19,380
Let's get to know
each other better tomorrow.

156
00:07:20,380 --> 00:07:20,910
Good night.

157
00:07:23,590 --> 00:07:24,180
Um...

158
00:07:25,540 --> 00:07:26,540
