162
00:08:16,020 --> 00:08:17,860
He thinks we're
too loud when we play games.

163
00:08:17,910 --> 00:08:19,060
He says it affects his karma.

164
00:08:19,230 --> 00:08:20,380
So he went to the lake

165
00:08:20,670 --> 00:08:21,470
to chant scriptures.

166
00:08:22,180 --> 00:08:22,590
Fine.

167
00:08:23,620 --> 00:08:25,740
Tonight, the student councils
from various faculties

168
00:08:25,740 --> 00:08:26,910
are hosting a big social event.

169
00:08:26,910 --> 00:08:28,580
They're having a barbecue.
Are you coming?

170
00:08:28,990 --> 00:08:29,380
Yes!

171
00:08:30,220 --> 00:08:31,120
Jing, what about you?

172
00:08:31,300 --> 00:08:31,670
No.

173
00:08:32,500 --> 00:08:32,900
Jing.

174
00:08:33,620 --> 00:08:35,860
I heard you've been trending
on the school forum.

175
00:08:36,140 --> 00:08:38,260
