to meet more people?

176
00:08:39,620 --> 00:08:40,470
Expanding your network

177
00:08:40,470 --> 00:08:42,300
is just as important
as studying seriously.

178
00:08:42,780 --> 00:08:43,190
No need.

179
00:08:44,350 --> 00:08:44,710
Jing.

180
00:08:45,830 --> 00:08:46,470
Just go.

181
00:08:47,380 --> 00:08:49,070
