185
00:08:52,310 --> 00:08:52,900
Catch.

186
00:08:53,060 --> 00:08:54,400
Then I'm definitely not going.

187
00:08:54,540 --> 00:08:55,500
Come on, Jing.

188
00:08:55,500 --> 00:08:56,620
Do me a favor.

189
00:08:56,830 --> 00:08:57,230
No.

190
00:08:57,380 --> 00:08:58,600
Are you really not going?

191
00:08:58,710 --> 00:08:59,140
No.

192
00:08:59,280 --> 00:09:00,480
Then we're heading out.

193
00:09:02,120 --> 00:09:02,840
Let's go.

194
00:09:03,350 --> 00:09:03,740
Let's go.

195
00:09:07,380 --> 00:09:08,860
What a pity.

196
00:09:16,100 --> 00:09:18,440
(Have you packed? Our dorm doesn't
have air conditioning. Does yours?)

197
00:09:18,440 --> 00:09:20,380
(Also, let's have dinner tonight.)
(Are you still mad?)

198
00:09:22,080 --> 00:09:22,880
What are you doing?

199
00:09:22,960 --> 00:09:23,540
Chen Huan'er.

200
00:09:23,940 --> 00:09:24,740
Hurry up and pack.

201
00:09:26,020 --> 00:09:26,860
