you should put on some makeup

205
00:09:31,590 --> 00:09:32,470
and change clothes.

206
00:09:33,950 --> 00:09:34,900
Is this not okay?

207
00:09:35,070 --> 00:09:36,190
Chen Huan'er.

208
00:09:36,300 --> 00:09:38,820
Are you really planning
to just show up like this for dinner?

209
00:09:38,860 --> 00:09:39,740
Isn't it just

210
00:09:39,740 --> 00:09:40,860
a casual gathering?

211
00:09:41,230 --> 00:09:43,020
This isn't an ordinary dinner.

212
00:09:43,380 --> 00:09:45,220
It's your first time
meeting the seniors.

213
00:09:45,220 --> 00:09:46,900
You need to make a good impression.

214
00:09:47,400 --> 00:09:49,500
Even if you don't want
to join the student council,

215
00:09:49,590 --> 00:09:50,140
