219
00:09:57,740 --> 00:09:58,800
Press your lips together.

220
00:09:59,120 --> 00:10:00,020
Put this on as well.

221
00:10:00,900 --> 00:10:02,190
Fine, you both...

222
00:10:02,470 --> 00:10:02,900
Hurry up.

223
00:10:04,660 --> 00:10:05,470
Let me see.

224
00:10:05,500 --> 00:10:06,220
Are you satisfied?

225
00:10:06,230 --> 00:10:06,590
Yes.

226
00:10:07,830 --> 00:10:09,110
Let's go.

227
00:10:09,310 --> 00:10:10,260
We're running late!

228
00:10:10,500 --> 00:10:10,900
Well.

229
00:10:11,620 --> 00:10:12,260
First of all,

230
00:10:12,310 --> 00:10:12,900
welcome

231
00:10:13,020 --> 00:10:14,260
to today's gathering!

232
00:10:14,780 --> 00:10:15,430
I'll say

233
00:10:15,830 --> 00:10:16,830
a few words.

234
00:10:17,310 --> 00:10:18,260
I really hope you all

235
00:10:18,260 --> 00:10:19,760
consider joining our art department.

236
00:10:19,760 --> 00:10:20,470
Our department

237
00:10:20,500 --> 00:10:21,710
is full of handsome guys

238
00:10:21,710 --> 00:10:22,900
and beautiful girls,

239
00:10:22,940 --> 00:10:25,340
and it's the most popular department
of the student council.

240
00:10:25,590 --> 00:10:25,950
Right.

241
00:10:25,950 --> 00:10:26,860
Since you've spoken,

242
00:10:26,860 --> 00:10:28,710
I'll say a few words
for the sports department.

243
00:10:28,710 --> 00:10:30,470
We are pretty straightforward.

244
00:10:30,660 --> 00:10:31,830
Tonight, I just want everyone

245
00:10:31,830 --> 00:10:32,840
to eat well, drink well,

246
00:10:32,880 --> 00:10:33,740
and have a great time!

247
00:10:33,740 --> 00:10:34,100
Nice!

248
00:10:34,100 --> 00:10:34,740
Great! Great!

249
00:10:34,950 --> 00:10:35,540
Great! Great!

250
00:10:35,830 --> 00:10:36,310
Good!

251
00:10:36,470 --> 00:10:37,230
Good!

252
00:10:41,190 --> 00:10:41,740
Tian Chi.

253
00:10:42,110 --> 00:10:42,620
Cheers.

254
00:10:42,740 --> 00:10:43,260
Cheers.

255
00:10:43,260 --> 00:10:44,100
Nice to meet you.

256
00:10:44,160 --> 00:10:45,020
Don't drink alone.

257
00:10:45,020 --> 00:10:45,800
I'll drink with you.

258
00:10:45,820 --> 00:10:46,310
All right.

259
00:10:47,590 --> 00:10:48,830
