260
00:10:48,900 --> 00:10:49,710
Be ladylike.

261
00:10:50,040 --> 00:10:51,430
Look at the good stuff I bought.

262
00:10:51,900 --> 00:10:52,430
Here.

263
00:10:52,430 --> 00:10:52,900
Be ladylike.

264
00:10:53,310 --> 00:10:53,950
Try this.

265
00:10:54,020 --> 00:10:54,430
Thanks.

266
00:10:55,230 --> 00:10:55,990
Huan'er?

267
00:10:56,540 --> 00:10:57,230
Senior Tian Chi?

268
00:10:58,430 --> 00:10:59,140
