269
00:10:59,990 --> 00:11:01,430
I'm in the student council.

270
00:11:01,430 --> 00:11:02,190
I was busy earlier,

271
00:11:02,200 --> 00:11:03,500
but I came over once I was done.

272
00:11:05,430 --> 00:11:06,470
Do you want a skewer?

273
00:11:06,740 --> 00:11:07,070
Here.

274
00:11:07,430 --> 00:11:08,190
Thanks.

275
00:11:13,260 --> 00:11:14,580
