305
00:12:35,260 --> 00:12:37,020
You can really hold your liquor.

306
00:12:39,540 --> 00:12:40,350
Drink up!

307
00:12:40,990 --> 00:12:41,740
Drink more!

308
00:12:41,740 --> 00:12:42,260
Come on.

309
00:12:42,260 --> 00:12:43,070
More!

310
00:12:44,380 --> 00:12:45,590
