324
00:13:11,380 --> 00:13:11,860
Goodness.

325
00:13:11,920 --> 00:13:13,160
Who does she take after?

326
00:13:13,620 --> 00:13:15,110
Call Xichi and ask him.

327
00:13:15,160 --> 00:13:16,120
She's probably fine.

328
00:13:16,310 --> 00:13:17,020
Right, good idea.

329
00:13:17,070 --> 00:13:18,950
I'll call Xichi.

330
00:13:20,540 --> 00:13:22,060
