338
00:13:38,140 --> 00:13:39,860
Could something have happened to her?

339
00:13:42,140 --> 00:13:43,230
What's wrong?

340
00:13:43,600 --> 00:13:44,720
Is Chen Huan'er unreachable?

341
00:13:45,830 --> 00:13:47,470
I've been calling,
