342
00:13:47,710 --> 00:13:49,350
Xichi, can you find her?

343
00:13:50,230 --> 00:13:50,740
Okay.

344
00:13:51,020 --> 00:13:51,620
Don't panic.

345
00:13:51,710 --> 00:13:52,440
I'll ask around.

346
00:13:52,540 --> 00:13:53,230
Okay.

347
00:14:10,470 --> 00:14:11,470
What's going on?

348
00:14:11,780 --> 00:14:12,260
Huan'er.

349
00:14:12,710 --> 00:14:13,230
Huan'er.

350
00:14:13,900 --> 00:14:14,350
Huan'er.

351
00:14:14,400 --> 00:14:15,230
Are you all right?

352
00:14:16,160 --> 00:14:17,190
Do you want some water?

353
00:14:17,500 --> 00:14:17,950
These...

354
00:14:18,020 --> 00:14:19,710
