355
00:14:20,340 --> 00:14:21,990
This alcohol has a strong aftereffect.

356
00:14:22,360 --> 00:14:23,110
Is she all right?

357
00:14:23,110 --> 00:14:23,590
Huan'er.

358
00:14:23,590 --> 00:14:24,350
What should we do?

359
00:14:24,440 --> 00:14:25,520
Let her drink some water.

360
00:14:25,710 --> 00:14:26,140
Huan'er.

361
00:14:39,430 --> 00:14:40,260
I feel dizzy.

362
00:14:40,990 --> 00:14:41,620
Chen Huan'er.

363
00:14:42,260 --> 00:14:43,260
Your mother called you.

364
00:14:43,260 --> 00:14:44,040
Where's your phone?

365
00:14:48,190 --> 00:14:48,860
My phone...

366
00:14:49,230 --> 00:14:50,020
My phone...

367
00:14:50,900 --> 00:14:51,830
My phone...

368
00:14:52,430 --> 00:14:53,430
It's in

369
00:14:54,470 --> 00:14:55,380
