370
00:14:55,470 --> 00:14:56,260
Right. It's here.

371
00:14:56,950 --> 00:14:57,710
It's here.

372
00:14:58,140 --> 00:14:59,620
It's in the bag.

373
00:15:02,140 --> 00:15:03,110
I found it.

374
00:15:03,470 --> 00:15:04,230
Sorry.

375
00:15:04,500 --> 00:15:05,820
Her alcohol tolerance isn't great.

376
00:15:06,020 --> 00:15:06,830
We'll leave first.

377
00:15:07,470 --> 00:15:08,350
No battery.

378
00:15:08,620 --> 00:15:09,620
My phone's dead.

379
00:15:09,620 --> 00:15:10,820
Charge it when we get back.

380
00:15:10,830 --> 00:15:11,380
Let's go.

381
00:15:11,620 --> 00:15:13,380
We're heading off too, Qiu Li.

382
00:15:13,380 --> 00:15:14,660
We'll leave now.

383
00:15:14,680 --> 00:15:16,120
We're going back to the girls' dorm.

384
00:15:16,160 --> 00:15:16,680
Goodbye.

385
00:15:17,310 --> 00:15:18,260
Hey, pass me the bag.

386
00:15:18,260 --> 00:15:18,780
Keep up!

387
00:15:18,780 --> 00:15:19,470
Be careful.

388
00:15:19,470 --> 00:15:20,350
Watch out.

389
00:15:20,500 --> 00:15:21,310
I'll help her.

390
00:15:21,990 --> 00:15:22,620
Slow down.

391
00:15:22,640 --> 00:15:24,020
- Watch the stairs.
- Is she okay?

392
00:15:24,040 --> 00:15:25,740
How did she get this drunk so fast?

393
00:15:27,070 --> 00:15:27,540
Slow down.

394
00:15:27,780 --> 00:15:28,470
Be careful.

395
00:15:28,500 --> 00:15:29,520
Let's take her there

396
00:15:29,520 --> 00:15:30,260
to rest for a bit

397
00:15:30,260 --> 00:15:31,160
before heading back.

398
00:15:31,310 --> 00:15:32,190
Slow down.

399
00:15:32,350 --> 00:15:33,070
Let's go there.

400
00:15:34,190 --> 00:15:34,710
All right.

401
00:15:34,780 --> 00:15:35,860
Don't touch me.

402
00:15:35,900 --> 00:15:37,180
- I'm all right.
- Be careful.

403
00:15:37,780 --> 00:15:38,860
Other than feeling dizzy,

404
00:15:38,900 --> 00:15:40,260
