405
00:15:40,380 --> 00:15:40,950
I'm okay.

406
00:15:41,190 --> 00:15:41,740
Really?

407
00:15:41,950 --> 00:15:42,710
Yes.

408
00:15:44,110 --> 00:15:44,740
Lu.

409
00:15:45,020 --> 00:15:46,500
I want to go back to use the bathroom.

410
00:15:46,580 --> 00:15:47,680
Number one or number two?

411
00:15:49,900 --> 00:15:50,860
You could go back first.

412
00:15:50,980 --> 00:15:52,760
I'll sit here with her
until she sobers up,

413
00:15:52,830 --> 00:15:53,740
then send her back.

414
00:15:53,990 --> 00:15:54,350
Okay.

415
00:15:54,500 --> 00:15:55,140
Wait.

416
00:15:55,590 --> 00:15:56,540
Leaving her alone here

417
00:15:56,540 --> 00:15:57,460
doesn't seem right.

418
00:15:57,710 --> 00:15:58,950
I really can't hold it anymore.

419
00:15:59,190 --> 00:16:00,380
I really can't.

420
00:16:02,950 --> 00:16:03,590
Aunt Lina.

421
00:16:04,380 --> 00:16:05,540
Don't worry, I found Huan'er.

422
00:16:05,540 --> 00:16:06,860
Her parents know him.

423
00:16:07,020 --> 00:16:07,660
Okay.

424
00:16:10,660 --> 00:16:12,780
I'll take her back first.

425
00:16:12,820 --> 00:16:13,830
Please take care of her.

426
00:16:14,070 --> 00:16:14,470
Okay.

427
00:16:14,470 --> 00:16:14,860
All right.

428
00:16:14,960 --> 00:16:16,260
Huan'er, we're heading off now.

429
00:16:17,230 --> 00:16:18,380
I need to go to the bathroom.

430
00:16:18,660 --> 00:16:19,190
It's fine.

431
00:16:19,230 --> 00:16:19,830
Just go back.

432
00:16:19,860 --> 00:16:20,230
Okay.

433
00:16:20,260 --> 00:16:20,830
Goodbye.

434
00:16:20,830 --> 00:16:21,990
Okay. Please take care of her.

435
00:16:21,990 --> 00:16:22,420
Goodbye.

436
00:16:22,420 --> 00:16:23,280
I'll leave her to you.

437
00:16:23,300 --> 00:16:24,280
Call me when you're back.

438
00:16:24,340 --> 00:16:25,620
It's okay. I can go back myself.

439
00:16:30,960 --> 00:16:31,990
Can you walk by yourself?

440
00:16:35,380 --> 00:16:35,900
Yes.

441
00:16:38,430 --> 00:16:39,860
Isn't that the dorm right there?

442
00:16:41,310 --> 00:16:42,110
I can make it.

443
00:16:47,990 --> 00:16:49,380
Can you? Are you sure?

444
00:16:49,620 --> 00:16:49,990
Get on.

445
00:16:52,660 --> 00:16:53,380
Just get on.

446
00:16:53,830 --> 00:16:54,900
You're poking me. It hurts.

447
00:16:55,740 --> 00:16:56,780
I feel like throwing up.

448
00:16:57,190 --> 00:16:58,380
Just don't throw up on me!

449
00:17:09,230 --> 00:17:10,230
Jing Xichi.

450
00:17:14,630 --> 00:17:15,260
What now?

451
00:17:17,740 --> 00:17:19,150
Take this punch from me.

452
00:17:19,160 --> 00:17:20,910
Can you stop making people
worry about you?

453
00:17:20,910 --> 00:17:21,820
Chen Huan'er!

454
00:17:22,990 --> 00:17:24,190
Drinking with strangers

455
00:17:24,230 --> 00:17:25,400
and getting this drunk,

456
00:17:25,470 --> 00:17:26,230
are you careless

457
00:17:26,230 --> 00:17:26,910
or just stupid?

458
00:17:28,710 --> 00:17:30,300
Yes, I'm just stupid.

459
00:17:31,580 --> 00:17:33,020
I'm an idiot.

460
00:17:34,500 --> 00:17:36,150
That's why I let
you fool me for so long.

461
00:17:37,670 --> 00:17:39,910
I just wanted to joke with you

462
00:17:39,950 --> 00:17:40,740
and give you

463
00:17:40,740 --> 00:17:41,710
a surprise.

464
00:17:41,990 --> 00:17:43,300
A joke is only a joke

465
00:17:43,820 --> 00:17:45,870
when both people

466
00:17:46,580 --> 00:17:47,950
find it funny.

467
00:17:48,260 --> 00:17:49,300
Do you get that?

468
00:17:52,260 --> 00:17:52,870
Fine.

469
00:17:53,190 --> 00:17:54,230
I'll apologize.

470
00:17:54,740 --> 00:17:55,260
I'm sorry.

471
00:17:55,740 --> 00:17:56,340
Okay?

472
00:17:57,910 --> 00:17:59,540
Can you stop being

473
00:17:59,540 --> 00:18:00,190
so childish,

474
00:18:00,230 --> 00:18:01,100
Jing Xichi?

475
00:18:02,990 --> 00:18:04,190
Are you saying I'm childish?

476
00:18:04,950 --> 00:18:06,540
Does going to that social event

477
00:18:07,100 --> 00:18:08,020
and getting drunk

478
00:18:08,060 --> 00:18:09,200
the first time you drink

479
00:18:09,260 --> 00:18:10,150
make you mature?

480
00:18:10,500 --> 00:18:11,870
We're not in high school anymore.

481
00:18:11,950 --> 00:18:12,910
We're in university.

482
00:18:13,740 --> 00:18:15,430
I can't just stay by your side

483
00:18:15,430 --> 00:18:17,340
all the time like before.

484
00:18:18,470 --> 00:18:19,740
Can you stop caring about me?

485
00:18:21,740 --> 00:18:23,260
If I don't, who will?

486
00:18:23,500 --> 00:18:24,470
If Aunt Lina

487
00:18:24,470 --> 00:18:25,190
hadn't called me,

488
00:18:25,950 --> 00:18:26,500
I...

489
00:18:26,740 --> 00:18:28,060
I wouldn't have bothered.

490
00:18:30,740 --> 00:18:31,260
Fine!

491
00:18:31,740 --> 00:18:32,710
From now on,

492
00:18:33,950 --> 00:18:35,500
we'll go

493
00:18:35,780 --> 00:18:36,630
our separate ways.

494
00:18:37,260 --> 00:18:38,740
Don't care about me anymore.

495
00:18:39,710 --> 00:18:40,780
I'll go back myself.

496
00:18:40,840 --> 00:18:42,240
How are you going to walk like this?

497
00:18:42,260 --> 00:18:43,440
Why wouldn't I be able to walk?

498
00:18:43,440 --> 00:18:44,230
I can walk! I...

499
00:18:44,670 --> 00:18:45,230
I can walk.

500
00:18:45,670 --> 00:18:47,260
I... I can walk.

501
00:18:51,230 --> 00:18:52,630
You seem to be on a shaky bridge.

502
00:18:52,960 --> 00:18:54,880
Didn't you say you don't care about me?

503
00:18:56,340 --> 00:18:57,740
Were you drinking fake alcohol?

504
00:19:12,300 --> 00:19:12,910
Hello.

505
00:19:25,820 --> 00:19:28,670
Today is the first class

506
00:19:28,820 --> 00:19:29,780
of Medical Psychology.

507
00:19:29,990 --> 00:19:31,300
I won't be taking attendance.

508
00:19:31,870 --> 00:19:32,580
There's no need

509
00:19:32,910 --> 00:19:34,630
for these formalities.

510
00:19:35,470 --> 00:19:36,500
Everyone

511
00:19:36,500 --> 00:19:37,820
seated in this hall today,

512
00:19:37,950 --> 00:19:38,870
I trust you all

513
00:19:39,820 --> 00:19:41,100
have a certain level

514
00:19:41,160 --> 00:19:42,060
of self-discipline.

515
00:19:42,630 --> 00:19:45,740
Those who chose clinical medicine

516
00:19:46,470 --> 00:19:48,100
aren't here

517
00:19:48,190 --> 00:19:49,470
to enjoy life.

518
00:19:49,710 --> 00:19:51,470
Do we all agree on that?

519
00:19:52,670 --> 00:19:53,740
Enough talk,

520
00:19:53,780 --> 00:19:55,020
let's get straight to class.

521
00:20:02,980 --> 00:20:03,860
My stomach hurts.

522
00:20:09,150 --> 00:20:10,060
You're awake.

523
00:20:12,390 --> 00:20:13,540
Drink some honey water.

524
00:20:13,600 --> 00:20:15,040
You drank too much last night.

525
00:20:16,230 --> 00:20:17,390
Li, thanks for saving

526
00:20:17,910 --> 00:20:18,870
my life.

527
00:20:19,100 --> 00:20:20,720
Next time, don't be so foolish.

528
00:20:20,720 --> 00:20:22,060
If you can't drink, don't.

529
00:20:22,240 --> 00:20:23,780
Anyway, you were pretty impressive.

530
00:20:23,780 --> 00:20:25,190
You could get upstairs on your own.

531
00:20:28,430 --> 00:20:29,630
Last night,

532
00:20:29,630 --> 00:20:31,480
wasn't it you both who brought me back?

533
00:20:31,630 --> 00:20:32,740
Don't you remember?

534
00:21:03,150 --> 00:21:04,670
Chen Huan'er, what are you doing?

535
00:21:05,100 --> 00:21:06,150
This is my bed!

536
00:21:06,500 --> 00:21:07,340
Huang Lu!

537
00:21:07,470 --> 00:21:08,820
Come get her off my bed!

538
00:21:09,630 --> 00:21:10,340
Chen Huan'er!

539
00:21:10,630 --> 00:21:11,670
Tonight,

540
00:21:11,780 --> 00:21:13,100
you're staying with me.

541
00:21:23,950 --> 00:21:24,580
Thanks.

542
00:21:24,870 --> 00:21:25,540
Seriously,

543
00:21:25,740 --> 00:21:26,230
Huan'er,

544
00:21:26,500 --> 00:21:27,780
you're really strong.

545
00:21:28,300 --> 00:21:29,670
Last night, Qiu Li and I

546
00:21:29,670 --> 00:21:31,600
couldn't move you
no matter how hard we tried.

547
00:21:33,470 --> 00:21:34,500
I'm really sorry.

548
00:21:34,630 --> 00:21:35,430
I had no idea

549
00:21:35,540 --> 00:21:36,500
I get this strong

550
00:21:37,020 --> 00:21:37,950
when I'm drunk.

551
00:21:39,300 --> 00:21:39,780
By the way,

552
00:21:40,340 --> 00:21:41,340
last night,

553
00:21:41,950 --> 00:21:42,780
did I do anything

554
00:21:42,820 --> 00:21:43,710
I shouldn't have?

555
00:21:44,340 --> 00:21:46,020
For that,

556
00:21:46,260 --> 00:21:47,500
you'll have to ask Jing.

557
00:21:48,360 --> 00:21:49,390
Why would I ask him?

558
00:21:49,460 --> 00:21:50,820
He's the one who brought you back.

559
00:21:56,390 --> 00:21:56,950
Was he...

560
00:21:57,710 --> 00:21:59,740
Was he there last night?

561
00:22:01,300 --> 00:22:03,060
What did you two do last night?

562
00:22:04,630 --> 00:22:06,190
Did he do something to you,

563
00:22:07,020 --> 00:22:08,470
or did you do something to him?

564
00:22:08,540 --> 00:22:09,300
No way!

565
00:22:09,300 --> 00:22:10,800
What could possibly happen between us?

566
00:22:10,800 --> 00:22:11,710
Don't overthink it.

567
00:22:12,340 --> 00:22:12,820
As expected,

568
00:22:13,150 --> 00:22:13,950
buddies

569
00:22:13,990 --> 00:22:15,390
can never become a couple.

570
00:22:16,300 --> 00:22:17,340
It's so warm.

571
00:22:17,430 --> 00:22:19,150
Who turned off the aircon again?

572
00:22:19,540 --> 00:22:20,430
Who else?

573
00:22:20,500 --> 00:22:21,540
It was the top student.

574
00:22:21,990 --> 00:22:24,020
I woke up at midnight from the heat

575
00:22:24,120 --> 00:22:25,910
and didn't fall back
asleep until after five.

576
00:22:26,020 --> 00:22:27,780
Every time she
comes back, she turns it off.

577
00:22:27,800 --> 00:22:29,460
If she doesn't like
air-conditioned rooms,

578
00:22:29,460 --> 00:22:31,500
why doesn't she move
to the old dorms in the east?

579
00:22:32,820 --> 00:22:33,630
Oh, right, Huan'er.

580
00:22:34,470 --> 00:22:35,430
Tian Chi

581
00:22:35,540 --> 00:22:36,710
called last night to ask

582
00:22:36,740 --> 00:22:37,780
how you were.

583
00:22:37,800 --> 00:22:38,780
You were already asleep,

584
00:22:38,780 --> 00:22:39,820
so I didn't wake you up.

585
00:22:39,990 --> 00:22:41,230
I charged your phone.

586
00:22:41,230 --> 00:22:41,990
Check your message.

587
00:22:42,150 --> 00:22:42,780
Thanks, Lu.

588
00:22:47,780 --> 00:22:48,500
(Are you okay?)

589
00:22:48,990 --> 00:22:50,300
(Huan'er, did you make it back?)

